node.text:
This is not your average flexibility class! & I hope that anyone who has taken one will tell you the same. The class is INTENSE‼️ It is CHALLENGING‼️There will be so many times that you want to quit‼️ But there will also be so many beautiful people there to encourage you to keep going! 

I put so much love & passion into every single class! I genuinely want nothing more, than to see each & every student progress! & learn & raise their body awareness! 

Y’all will see so much more of this! & hopefully you all get to experience it as well! 

🎥: @kareemchap 🔥☄️💥
Thank you for the amazing work! 🙏🏾

node.text:
I love my city! Leaving Chicago will be bittersweet for me. I want to thank each of y’all for coming and pushing through til the end! We had expectant mothers, kids, Men, & women of all ages, shapes, and sizes! 

I swear I will never get used to this! I am so grateful for each and every single one of you! 

NYC 📍 ATL 📍HOUSTON📍

Y’all got next! 😈 START HYDRATING NOWWWWWWWWWWWW

🎥: @ricer90 ☄️🔥💫

Soooo I lost between 2 & 3 inches on my waist in 5 days! 🥲 shoutout to Dr.Kim! 🙌🏾 @kim_keepitmoving for setting me up on her cleanse! Had to hop on live with her & talk about my personal experience. While she filled me all the way in on all the wonderful benefits. 

If you’re interest in trying the detox Click the link in her bio, but don’t forget to dm her & tell her I sent you for a gift with your purchase. ☺️

node.text:
Bend & Snap NYC 

“Y’all are gonna hate me in about 15minutes” 🤣🤣 that part is important! 

Still high from this trip! 😍 NYC never disappoints. The energy was everything! 

Thank you to everyone who has been a part of this tour! Online & in person. Thank y’all so much for allowing me to push you pass your limits. & then some! Lol. You know I do it all out of love! 🤎 & I am so grateful To have all of that love returned to me 🥰

Always blissful ✨

node.text:
I keep saying ima take a break, but y’all make it sooooo hard for me! 😩😅 I just been having too much fun! & I hope y’all have been too! 

After this last weekend in Chicago 🥺 (GET YOUR TICKETS NOW) I will be taking a few weeks off, but then I’m hopping right back in next month! 

How does Bend & Snap Las Vegas sound? 🙃💃🏾 

Link in bio

📸: @reneechoiphotography & Charlee Valentine 💗

node.text:
This is not your average flexibility class! & I hope that anyone who has taken one will tell you the same. The class is INTENSE‼️ It is CHALLENGING‼️There will be so many times that you want to quit‼️ But there will also be so many beautiful people there to encourage you to keep going! 

I put so much love & passion into every single class! I genuinely want nothing more, than to see each & every student progress! & learn & raise their body awareness! 

Y’all will see so much more of this! & hopefully you all get to experience it as well! 

🎥: @kareemchap 🔥☄️💥
Thank you for the amazing work! 🙏🏾

node.text:
Bend & Snap Tour ✨

ATL 📍 Saturday August 14th

HOUSTON 📍 Sunday August 15th

Another weekend; two more cities; & so many more people to S T R E T C H ! I can’t wait to get my hands on yall 😈Come nothing short of HYDRATED 😤 ‼️ 

You’ll need every drop 🥲 

Link in bio ✨

 📸 photo snapped by @reneechoiphotography 🌟

node.text:
Bend & Snap is for every BODY! 😤 Look at all of these beautiful people of all shapes & sizes & shades & genders! Most of them doubting their capabilities! But when you have a room full of beautiful energy, there’s no room for doubt! Someone, EVERYONE is gonna encourage you! & you will do things you never thought you could! 

NYC I miss y’all already! 😩 I can never thank y’all enough for trusting me with y’all bodies! I can never thank y’all enough for the growing love & support that I continue to receive! I genuinely love each & every single one of y’all to my core! & I promise that I have so much more to give 🥲🤎

📸: photos by @reneechoiphotography 💫 ✨

node.text:
I love my city! Leaving Chicago will be bittersweet for me. I want to thank each of y’all for coming and pushing through til the end! We had expectant mothers, kids, Men, & women of all ages, shapes, and sizes! 

I swear I will never get used to this! I am so grateful for each and every single one of you! 

NYC 📍 ATL 📍HOUSTON📍

Y’all got next! 😈 START HYDRATING NOWWWWWWWWWWWW

🎥: @ricer90 ☄️🔥💫
